t: Try to move the pieces above each other & see which go above which. Then press [Ctrl]+[3] or [Alt]+[3] for the next tutorial!
Toggle the layers via the top-left menu icons or press the [1], [2], [3] or [4] hotkeys.
You can't select or manipulate pieces if their layer is not active. 'Overlays' and 'Tiles' are OFF by default.
Other than sticky notes, there are four types of game pieces ...
